1092
01:25:46,837 --> 01:25:47,272
Não?

1093
01:25:47,403 --> 01:25:49,187
OK.

1094
01:26:20,087 --> 01:26:21,219
Eu adoro isso aqui.

1095
01:26:26,920 --> 01:26:28,879
